This is an open-source project created by Bruce Kroeze <bruce@ecomsmith.com> for Black Rock City LLC.  It is copyright 2011, Black Rock City LLC.

The project is a split of functionality previously found in "Burning Man Earth", with quite a few changes, increased security, and an extended API.

To take gifting and collaboration beyond Black Rock City and into the digital realm, the software and APIs are available open-source under the Apache License <http://code.burningman.com/documents/7>.

